java.lang.Object

public class Padstack extends Object implements Comparable<Padstack>, ObjectInfoPanel.Printable, Serializable
Describes padstack masks for pins or vias located at the origin.

      public final boolean placed_absolute

    • get_trace_exit_directions

      public Collection<Direction> get_trace_exit_directions(int p_layer, double p_factor)
      Calculates the allowed trace exit directions of the shape of this padstack on layer p_layer. If the length of the pad is smaller than p_factor times the height of the pad, connection also to the long side is allowed.
